<% layout("./layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Locatify Logo" style="max-height: 120px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                <h1 class="display-4">About Locatify</h1>
                <p class="lead text-muted">Discover, book, and manage unique places to stay.</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Locatify</strong> is a full-stack web application inspired by Airbnb, designed to provide a seamless experience for users to discover, book, and manage vacation rentals. Our platform is built with a passion for travel and technology, aiming to connect hosts with travelers from around the world.</p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-5">Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to make finding the perfect place to stay simple, intuitive, and enjoyable. Whether you're looking for a cozy room in a bustling city, a serene cabin in the mountains, or a luxurious castle, Locatify helps you find your next adventure.</p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-5">Key Features</h2>
            <p>We've packed Locatify with features to enhance your experience:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Interactive Maps:</strong> Powered by OpenStreetMap, every listing shows its location, helping you explore the neighborhood before you book.</li>
                <li><strong>User Reviews & Ratings:</strong> Make informed decisions with genuine reviews and a 5-star rating system from fellow travelers.</li>
                <li><strong>Secure Image Uploads:</strong> Hosts can easily upload high-quality images of their properties, managed securely via Cloudinary.</li>
                <li><strong>Modern & Responsive UI:</strong> Enjoy a clean, Airbnb-inspired design that works beautifully on any device, from desktops to mobile phones.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-5">The Technology Behind Locatify</h2>
            <p>Locatify is built using a modern stack of web technologies to ensure a robust and scalable platform:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB with Mongoose</li>
                <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> EJS, Bootstrap 5, and Vanilla JavaScript</li>
                <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Passport.js for secure user registration and login.</li>
                <li><strong>And more:</strong> Including Cloudinary for image management and NodeGeocoder for location services.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="mt-5 text-center">Thank you for being a part of the Locatify community. Happy travels!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>